OL,3,CSome young British adults replacing
OL,4,Cturkey with curry or pizza this
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FYounger British adults are forsaking
OL,8,Fthe traditional Christmas dinner, with
OL,9,Falmost a fifth saying they will be
OL,10,Fserving up the likes of curry, pasta
OL,11,For pizza instead this year.
OL,13,FSome 17% of those aged 25 to 34 are
OL,14,Fturning away from the traditional
OL,15,Fturkey and all the trimmings in favour
OL,16,Fof "mixing things up" with non-
OL,17,Ftraditional fare, according to Tesco's
OL,18,Fannual Christmas Trends Report, based
OL,19,Fon a survey and sales figures.
