OL,7,FJust 52% of adults of all ages plan to
OL,8,Fserve turkey this Christmas, with 23%
OL,9,Fopting for chicken, 20% turning to
OL,10,Fbeef and 21% preparing a plant-based
OL,11,Fmenu.
OL,13,FWhile pigs in blankets is the best-
OL,14,Floved trimming among all adults, only
OL,15,F22% of those aged 25 to 34 would say
OL,16,Fthe same, preferring rice (32%) or
OL,17,Feven chips (23%).
